
This repository contains the recipes for interspeech2017

Note:
1. By default, config_syn.cfg in each directory will generate the F0 
   by using the one-best generation method.

2. To use soft generation method, please modify config_syn.cfg according to
    ./config_syn_soft.py

3. To use random sampling, please modify config_syn.cfg according to 
    ./config_syn_random.py